<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy-Checker | Profile</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="afterstyle.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700;800&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col bg-gray-900 text-white font-poppins">

    <div class="relative w-full min-h-screen overflow-hidden">
        <header class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full flex justify-between items-center py-4 px-8 z-50 bg-gray-950/80 backdrop-blur">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-cyan-400">Privacy-Checker</div>
            <nav>
                <ul class="flex space-x-8">
                    <li><a href="/" class="text-cyan-300 hover:text-white transition text-lg">Back to Main</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </header>

        <main class="flex-grow pt-32 pb-16 px-6 md:px-12">
            <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-gray-800 p-10 rounded-xl shadow-xl border border-cyan-500">
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8 text-center">Your Analyzed Websites</h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-10 text-center">A simple list of sites you've explored with summaries below.</p>

                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                    <div class="bg-gray-700 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-600">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-cyan-300 mb-2">example.com</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-200">Transparent policies. Minimal tracking. Low risk.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-700 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-600">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-cyan-300 mb-2">socialnet.ai</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-200">Shares user behavior data with affiliates. Exercise caution.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-700 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-600">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-cyan-300 mb-2">shopncart.io</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-200">Extensive cookie usage for personalization. Optional opt-out.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>

        <footer class="w-full py-6 text-center text-gray-400 text-sm bg-gray-950 border-t border-gray-700">
            &copy; 2025 Privacy-Checker. All rights reserved.
        </footer>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
